{"tid":1653450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［大家識做啦］梁愛詩：禁蒙面法後示威人數減","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T06:17:33.000Z","uid":216992,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95456e4425f76f9cf8d18c7cbd23e2f8bbe38811","tid":1653450,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩不認同禁蒙面法有反效果，認為雖然仍有暴力衝擊，但示威人數已減少，又指新例的限制合理。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩：「如果說完全禁止戴面罩，這個是不合理，這個是不合理的限制，但是如果在一個場合，遊行、示威無論合法、非法的場合，這些每每結果是發生暴力，在此時政府作出這個限制，我覺得是合理的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366177&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=1441fcaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366177&h=a97b89c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366177</a>"},{"pid":"16665d2861d3953390cb2a663b6d747df2c568ff","tid":1653450,"uid":209543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c80cf8f1f85325a4748aae41d16eab7b16902a0c","tid":1653450,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"193f8b1afd8cc7dcf7c098b85831042bc83e014c","tid":1653450,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"呢條廢老應該612一早收佢皮"},{"pid":"914dd47ceae3c416a8e542d475ba1c62391b86d9","tid":1653450,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"係時候了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6569b0fff81651d132a71dad3c2bc2e9bd2ab9c0","tid":1653450,"uid":312242,"like":1,"dislik